title: BIG 4 BDRM in a "small village" atmosphere! ... You'll love it !
posting_body: ['In the quaint yet modern charming town of Dupont, this 2 story 4 bedroom home is ready for your family and enjoys an "End of the road" location that ensures your peace and quiet enjoyment.', 'Main Floor:', '- "open concept"', '- SPACIOUS living room with gas fireplace', '- LARGE dining area off the kitchen with sliding door to small rear yard', '- kitchen has plenty of counter space and cabinets', '- LARGE PANTRY off kitchen', '- 1/2 bath "powder room"', '- 2 car garage with auto opener', 'Upper Floor:', '- MASTER BEDROOM SUITE - HUGE16 x 16 bedroom, spacious 5 x 14 walk-in closet and big master bathroom with', 'double sinks and separate tub & shower.', '- 3 more bedrooms', '- full bathroom', '- laundry room with W/D hook-ups', 'VACANT and ready NOW!', 'RENT       =  $2,495 / month', 'DEPOSIT = $ 2,800', 'Address - 3533 Hoffman Hill Blvd, Dupont, WA, 98327', 'INTERESTED?', 'Good!', 'You might want to start by   DRIVING BY  &  WALKING AROUND :', 'It’s vacant so you are free to walk around and check the place out from the outside.', 'PRE-SCREENING :', 'You might want to pre-screen yourself a bit… before you spend $50 and apply:', 'GO to our website at    <URL>,  CLICK on “AM I APPROVABLE?”', 'in the toolbar and  “TAKE THE TEST” to see if your application might be approvable before you spend $50 to apply,  …  but you still must actually APPLY to really find out!', 'APPLYING :', 'With the demand SO HIGH for rental homes these days,  some people go ahead and APPLY before seeing the inside of the property... to get your application "first in line", so to speak.', ' Even if you are approved you will STILL NEED TO GO SEE the property for you “final acceptance” of it.', 'A.  Go to our website and CLICK on “AVAILABLE” in the toolbar,', 'B.  FIND THE HOME you are interested in and', 'C.  CLICK on “APPLY NOW” on the far-right side where you can APPLY and PAY', 'the $50/adult application fee ONLINE with a credit card.', 'VIEWING :', 'If you PASSED THE PRE-SCREENING “TEST” and want to continue with the process then', 'CALL JANET  (our tenant support specialist)  at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a day & time for a showing.', 'Still have questions?', '  Want to schedule a viewing?', '      Call', 'show contact info', '.', 'We are Red Roof Rentals, LLC.', '     Open Mon – Fri,   10 AM - 5 PM…', 'and we thank you.']
